headline: Why EPAM (EPAM) Shares Are Trading Lower Today
summary: Shares of digital engineering services company EPAM Systems (NYSE:EPAM) fell 5.7% in the afternoon session after Morgan Stanley lowered its price target on the information technology services provider's stock.
